across time;\nthis rapid variation further illustrates that time-dependent models are needed\nfor operational analysis of ridesourcing systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Feb 2020 08:51:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 21:01:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-17"}
