ameters. Leaf-bifurcation varieties\nare derived. Leaf-bifurcations provides a venue for cell-bifurcation control of\ninvariant toral CW complexes. The results are implemented and verified using\nMaple for practical bifurcation control of such parametric nonlinear\noscillators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Feb 2020 18:47:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-26"}
